Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.98,0:11:03.47,FFF,+,0,0,0,,{\fs22\pos(625,180)}也按回答正确处理——
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.98,0:11:03.47,FFF,+,0,0,0,,{\pos(556,353)\1c&H82706F&\3c&H000000&}土屋康太的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.98,0:11:03.47,FFF,+,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(475,263)}『　　　　　　　　　  ←反白可见』
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.98,0:11:03.47,FFF,+,0,0,0,,{\pos(436,353)\1c&HFF9B86&\3c&H000000&}吉井明久的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.98,0:11:03.47,FFF,+,0,0,0,,{\fs25\pos(356,309)}『　　　　　　　　　  ←笨蛋是看不见答案的』
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.98,0:11:03.47,FFF,+,0,0,0,,{\pos(310,305)}教师点评
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:03.47,FFF,+,0,0,0,,{\fs24\pos(162,188)}——虽然是这样打算的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.06,0:11:03.47,FFF,+,0,0,0,,{\fs24\pos(136,157)}但你们两个例外
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:03.47,FFF,+,0,0,0,,{\fs24\pos(110,136}给你们零分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.45,0:11:09.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之后过了一个礼拜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.21,0:11:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,课程也正式开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.10,0:11:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对还没熟悉日语的我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.89,0:11:19.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现代国语到底在上什么完全听不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.15,0:11:22.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其是对于古典文学 更是难解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.72,0:11:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么吉井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.55,0:11:28.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种情况下「はべり」的活用形应该是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.13,0:11:31.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 「はんなり」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.38,0:11:36.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问你的是古文的活用形 回答的却是京都方言
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.60,0:11:40.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个风马牛不相及的搞笑回答呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.22,0:11:41.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？啊咧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.92,0:11:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么在下次上课之前请复习好今天学到的内容
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.80,0:12:01.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于完了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.08,0:12:06.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚想着总算能从拷问般无聊的课堂中解放出来的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.81,0:12:09.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岛田同学 要去哪里呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.13,0:12:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.25,0:12:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.84,0:12:14.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 要回家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.60,0:12:16.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 What a Sea？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,wa ta shi （我）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.52,0:12:23.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 原来是说了我要回家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.90,0:12:26.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉没有听清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.21,0:12:28.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岛田同学刚从外国回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.35,0:12:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为说的是外语呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.20,0:12:40.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于还没习惯日语的我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.71,0:12:43.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没能理解他那快语速的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.99,0:12:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然想要努力去理解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.62,0:12:48.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是大脑跟不上 好像要爆炸一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.72,0:12:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…虽然我也很想回家 但是还不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.55,0:12:55.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为之后还有班会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.49,0:13:01.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 现在还不能回去 再等一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.62,0:13:05.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙在笑什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.07,0:13:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会说日语就这么有趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.21,0:13:13.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:25.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在问「美波你中学的时候参加了什么社团」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.08,0:13:28.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是现在该问的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.49,0:13:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来这家伙的日语语法用对了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.45,0:13:43.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听不懂！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.95,0:13:54.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.71,0:13:59.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么大家都不理解我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.63,0:14:02.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明都这么努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.78,0:14:01.66,D2,+,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.99,0:14:05.12,D2,+,0,0,0,,欢迎回来的说 姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.33,0:14:09.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说大家都讨厌我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.67,0:14:07.30,D2,+,0,0,0,,学校怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.59,0:14:11.22,D2,+,0,0,0,,非常有趣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我其实不应该来这里的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.13,0:14:14.13,D2,+,0,0,0,,找到朋友了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.38,0:14:17.13,D2,+,0,0,0,,有很多不错的朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.38,0:14:18.63,D2,+,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.86,0:14:19.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.89,0:14:21.06,D2,+,0,0,0,,嗯 日本真是个好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.35,0:14:22.48,D2,+,0,0,0,,那真是太好了的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.66,0:14:41.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我仍然没能融入班级之中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.53,0:14:45.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不懂日语 没法交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.68,0:14:47.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以没有谈话对象
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.87,0:14:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是恶性循环
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.65,0:14:54.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最初那天给人的第一印象很差是原因所在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.06,0:14:59.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天从弄错名字的汉字开始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.39,0:15:09.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 这应该还是保持着错误的样子才对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.03,0:15:10.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.12,0:15:17.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 明久 开物中学毕业的家伙们说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要赌上小卖部的面包来场篮球赛 你怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.12,0:15:21.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要来要来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.25,0:15:23.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个月的伙食费很紧张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.45,0:15:24.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.77,0:15:26.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也让老夫参加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.07,0:15:28.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来好像很有趣的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.67,0:15:31.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙什么时候关系变那么好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.37,0:15:38.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tu ne voudrais pas devenir mon amie
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.46,0:15:42.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tu ne voudrais pas devenir mon amie
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.38,0:15:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊这家伙 又说些不明所以的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.67,0:15:50.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听不懂日语啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.79,0:15:53.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说monami是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.75,0:15:55.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不叫monami而是minami啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.69,0:15:59.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连我名字都记不住 别来套近乎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.72,0:16:03.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tu ne voudrais pas devenir mon amie
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.09,0:16:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tu ne…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.92,0:16:09.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别向我搭话 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.76,0:16:11.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「不要踢梨？」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.22,0:16:17.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「我 是 man. You are？」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.55,0:16:20.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.81,0:16:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是说岛田同学是男生？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.21,0:16:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙连英语都没法沟通吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.22,0:16:27.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What a shit man you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.66,0:16:29.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是对你很火大的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.13,0:16:31.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.10,0:16:33.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对着愤怒的女生叫她男人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.86,0:16:35.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胆子不小啊 明久
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.10,0:16:37.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这样的 岛田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.37,0:16:39.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不是因为岛田同学的胸部很小
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.18,0:16:40.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才认为岛田同学是个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.71,0:16:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不过是用我的常识来想的…疼啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.90,0:16:46.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不懂日语
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.95,0:16:48.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不知道为什么只有胸部很小
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.69,0:16:50.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那部分清楚地听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.33,0:16:53.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What a shit man you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.38,0:16:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.73,0:16:59.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.35,0:17:01.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不应该来日本的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.77,0:17:02.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 岛田
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.72,0:17:06.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是刚认识那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.18,0:17:07.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.59,0:17:09.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.66,0:17:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定是个非常有趣的家伙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.60,0:17:13.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Baka...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.85,0:17:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙说的话 去查查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.10,0:17:43.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 是说笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.55,0:17:44.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事情我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.89,0:17:51.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,jyunu budorepa...到底是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.45,0:17:54.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正肯定是在嘲笑我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.95,0:17:59.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查查那家伙在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.54,0:18:01.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后再反过来戏弄他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.51,0:18:05.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,jyunu budorepa
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.11,0:18:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,jyunu budorepa
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:09.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,jyunu budorepa
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.38,0:18:11.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找不到和这类似的单词
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.95,0:18:15.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙到底说了什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来那日语真的没用错吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.22,0:18:20.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明连我的名字都对不上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.47,0:18:22.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明不是monami而是minami啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.72,0:18:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,monami?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.03,0:18:31.73,D2,+,0,0,0,,{\pos(1220,580)}monami
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.20,0:18:32.95,D2,+,0,0,0,,{\pos(77,580)}monami
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.77,0:18:35.15,D2,+,0,0,0,,为什么都在叫我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.40,0:18:36.40,D2,+,0,0,0,,不是的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.65,0:18:40.16,D2,+,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\shad0}那不是minami而是mon amie
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.47,0:18:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.80,0:18:51.27,D2,+,0,0,0,,{\bord1}--美波 3岁 在法国--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.81,0:18:50.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法国
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.60,0:19:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tu ne voudrais pas devenir mon amie
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.92,0:19:21.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是日语啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.87,0:19:23.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且也不是德语
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:26.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙弄错了 去查的法语
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.66,0:19:29.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙真的是笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.05,0:19:35.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,图书馆里没有将法语直接翻译成德语的辞典
